3#ifndef __NVBIOS_EXTDEV_H__
4#define __NVBIOS_EXTDEV_H__
5enum nvbios_extdev_type {
6 NVBIOS_EXTDEV_LM89 = 0x02,
7 NVBIOS_EXTDEV_VT1103M = 0x40,
8 NVBIOS_EXTDEV_PX3540 = 0x41,
9 NVBIOS_EXTDEV_VT1105M = 0x42, /* or close enough... */
10 NVBIOS_EXTDEV_ADT7473 = 0x70, /* can also be a LM64 */
11 NVBIOS_EXTDEV_HDCP_EEPROM = 0x90,
12 NVBIOS_EXTDEV_NONE = 0xff,
13};
14
15struct nvbios_extdev_func {
16 u8 type;
17 u8 addr;
18 u8 bus;
19};
